Quote: GREY RIVER CONSOLIDATED DREDGING COMPANY. .. Mr A. J. Park moved, and Mr Thomson seconded-"That the directors be authorised to sell the amalgamated claim of the company to the new company, when formed, for GBP5000, and to accept fully paid-up shares in the new company in lieu of cash." - Carried unanimously.
